stimulusHtml: What, if anything, is printed as a result of executing the code segment?

features.html:
In the following code segment, assume that the  ArrayList  data  has been initialized to contain the  Integer  values  [4, 3, 4, 5, 3, 4].

 

int j = 0; 
while (j < data.size() - 1) 
{ 
   if (data.get(j) > data.get(j + 1)) 
   { 
      System.out.print(data.get(j + 1) + " "); 
   } 
   j++; 
}

choicesHtml: Nothing is printed because an  IndexOutOfBoundsException  occurs.
